{"word":"Sackcloth","slug":"sackcloth","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Sackcloth</b> A symbol of mourning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=20&verse=32'>1Ki 20:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=16&verse=15'>Job 16:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=15&verse=3'>Isa 15:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=4&verse=8'>Jer 4:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=6&verse=26'>Jer 6:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=49&verse=3'>Jer 49:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=25&chapter=2&verse=10'>Lam 2:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=7&verse=18'>Eze 7:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=9&verse=3'>Dan 9:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=29&chapter=1&verse=8'>Joe 1:8</a><br/> Worn by Jacob when it was reported to him that Joseph had been devoured by wild beasts<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=37&verse=34'>Gen 37:34</a><br/> Animals covered with, at time of national mourning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=32&chapter=3&verse=8'>Jon 3:8</a><br/><a href='S:Mourning'>Mourning</a>"}]}